For example:
```
<span class="tag">Bulma is a free, open source CSS framework based on Flexbox and used by more than 150,000 developers.</span>
```

How to break this on smaller layouts?

I tried these with no luck
```
overflow-wrap: break-word;
word-wrap: break-word;
word-break: break-word;
word-break: break-all;
```
